Madylin Sweeten https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madylin_Sweeten 0 Madylin Anne Michele Sweeten (born June 27, 1991) is an American actress and comedian, best known as a child star for playing the role of Ally Barone, the daughter of Ray and Debra on the CBS television sitcom Everybody Loves Raymond from 1996–2005.
